{"tid":1367132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集氣] 遍地開花 各界聯署綜合一覽","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T11:33:42.000Z","uid":275507,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63391dde68a32b2ed87e151088aaf2891b9c9df1","tid":1367132,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家繼續將聯署既力量散播到唔同行業，全港大罷工指日可待</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">巴打幫手補加唔同聯署既link，綜合各界力量幫大家打下氣鼓勵下各行各業既人企出來，整合各界力量，一步步推進</span><br />\n<br />\n77名將軍澳綫港鐵車長開名聯署，佔全綫85%<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366936</a><br />\n<br />\n超過 500 名熱愛香港的政府行政主任聯署公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366718/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366718/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n逾百 AO 聯署：守護香港核心價值，是我們加入政府的初衷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366878/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366878/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【代出】保險起動 Insurance ARISE 業界聯署聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366621/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366621/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【反修例】逾千專業人士聯署 促政府回應訴求緩精神健康危機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1332043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1332043</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 航空界聯合聲明｜致訪港旅客公開信 （附聯署圖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364828/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364828/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[繼續遍地開花］ 一群關心社會的香港童軍要求香港童軍總會就近日社會事件回應之聯署聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364276/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364276/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n逾320名公務員聯署 倘特首漠視民意將發起工業行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366521/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366521/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「拒暴力 全力緝兇 順民意 獨立調查」- 35名社會賢達再發動聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366318/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366318/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nAO 醞釀聯署促成立獨立調查委員會 報道指公務員事務局急會晤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366325/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366325/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 言語治療師聯署 促請政府積極回應及處理修例風波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1365384/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1365384/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【今次到醫護界】逾800名醫護聯署譴責警察缺乏職業道德<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366393/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366393/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n醫學教育界聯署 批港府聲明扭曲事實<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346869</a>"},{"pid":"448229f405e17d3cb9a88fa0e4300628c07ff77d","tid":1367132,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3ce190bb1a3a9bc20cc71f9e2d177b201bb338","tid":1367132,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35309716adb60c1fa90d334e2abf597fac5b323","tid":1367132,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n《生於亂世，有種責任》<br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd962994d479f762389773dfe0989d0d4e899911","tid":1367132,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"留名睇班藍屍出黎廢UP話全部係暴徒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454e2afad1274e6b12b6caadb0a67d